
#  For issues and requests, service level agreement
#  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#  SUPPORT AND COMMUNICATIONS / TIMELINES
#  ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

#  Email: zone-admin@protonmail.com


#  What to expect / our commitment : 

#  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#  SLA:                      Response                                  Resolution                           Communications availability                         
#  ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------



#  Business critical         1-hour to 4-hour response time            1-hour up to 48-hour resolution      Zoom support where required and email.             

#  Business add-ons          24-hour response time                     1-hour to 24 hours to resolution     Email.

#  Trial users               24-hour to 72-hour response time          6-hour to 24 hour resolution         Zoom support where required and email.







Note: Times are estimates for a particularly challenging day. We aim to answer requests faster than that in most cases. 
